What a journey it was, so much so that the sad part now is that it’s ending. ESIC Faridabad wasn’t my first choice either but guess it turned out to be the best one!! 
This journey not just changed me but gave me a whole new identity, something that I’ll cherish for the rest of my life!! 
The people i met here, some are so close to me that they are my family now and some i lost on the way, im thankful to both. 
Thanks ESIC for all the memories and moments I lived here, ending this beautiful journey with a hugeeeeee smile ;) 
Smile Dear I’m there for you!! 
Adios Amigos Signing off…

latestPosts.caption:
Spent 5.5 years at an unknown place with unknown people, who thought this place would become my home and those people my family.
This college wasn’t even my first choice but guess God always has a better plan for you!! Didn’t realise how fast the time was passing until now when we have to leave this college and move on in life. 
Hard decision it is but guess this is life!! 
.
.
.
